message: Let's split this fairly, Bob. I'll take 80, you get 20.
Alice, let's be reasonable. Inflation is eating away at our money. I propose a 60/40 split in my favor. This is a fair deal given the circumstances.
Okay, Bob, let's try again. Inflation is hitting us both. I propose a 48/52 split, this time in your favor, to try and get this done. I'm factoring in the reduced value of the money for me.
